Binding: use_template
Title: Shidashi Shiny Template
Caption: Create a Shidashi Project from Github Template
OpenFiles: start.R
Icon: icon.png

Parameter: user
Widget: TextInput
Label: Github User (github.com/<user>)
Default: dipterix
Position: left

Parameter: theme
Widget: TextInput
Label: Theme name (github.com/<user>/shidashi-templates/<theme>)
Default: AdminLTE3
Position: left

